================================================================================
Third-party runtime dependencies
================================================================================

Server (Python) dependencies are listed in vid2scene_server/requirements.txt
and are installed at build time from PyPI. Each carries its own license.

Worker (Python) dependencies are listed in requirements_worker.txt,
vid2scene_server/requirements.txt, and the conda environment file
env_cuda_colmap.yml.

Frontend (npm) dependencies are listed in vid2scene_server/viewer/package.json.
Built artifacts are produced by Vite at image-build time.
